title: Breaking Halfloop-24
Show HN: A GitHub Action to wait for jobs in step, helpful to prestart the job
text: Currently GitHub Actions doesn't have a native way (needs) to wait for jobs in a step. This action allows to wait for the specified jobs in the same run to be complete successfully before proceeding. Such a behavior is beneficial when dependee job has steps that can run/ finish before the job dependencies are completed or out from them is actually required
